title: Start
body:
*Yawn* Hi, can I help
you with something?
-> Do you know anything about this key?
    Nope, I've never seen
    anything like it. 
    -> Who runs this place?
        Hana, she hangs out
        at the top of the cafe. 
        Will you let me get back
        to my cat-nap, now?
        -> Thanks for the help.
*Yawn*
